{"type":"message","id":"1797a6ff","parentId":"82a483d4","timestamp":"2026-03-03T02:03:25.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想先完善数据层，策略想法是小市值策略。让我：\n1. 获取更完整的数据（包括财务数据、市值等）\n2. 专门为小市值策略准备数据\n\n小市值策略需要的数据：\n- 市值（total_market_cap）\n- 流通市值（float_market_cap）\n- 日线行情（获取价格计算收益率）\n\n让我先完善数据获取脚本，然后开始获取小市值策略需要的数据。","thinkingSignature":"7f9a95782d0c5e510d8e25aee81d4b62161204fde02d1b27a586302db42c32c5"},{"type":"text","text":"明白！小市值策略需要的数据主要是市值、流通市值、日线行情。让我完善数据层。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2dtflsbuic8d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && source .venv/bin/activate && python -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\nload_dotenv('config/.env.tushare')\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 测试获取市值数据\ndf = pro.daily_basic(ts_code='000001.SZ', start_date='20260101')\nprint('日线基本面字段:')\nprint(df.columns.tolist())\nprint(df.head())\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":257,"cacheRead":18402,"cacheWrite":8148,"totalTokens":26843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772503389231}}
