{"type":"message","id":"65cb92d5","parentId":"bbeafb11","timestamp":"2026-03-03T02:30:45.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"选股模块工作了！从500只股票样本中选出了25只小市值股票。\n\n现在让我再次尝试获取完整数据，使用一个更简单的方式。","thinkingSignature":"6dd886c97959746aa3f48ec6042adab5ab342c63dc7701248e7cbec3d555bec0"},{"type":"text","text":"选股模块已上线！现在让我继续获取完整数据：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tflidm86jfbj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && source .venv/bin/activate && python -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nimport time\n\npro = ts.pro_api('fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc')\nstocks = pd.read_csv('data/stock_basic.csv')['ts_code'].tolist()\n\nprint(f'获取 {len(stocks)} 只...')\nall_data = []\n\nfor i, code in enumerate(stocks):\n    try:\n        df = pro.daily_basic(ts_code=code, start_date='20250101', fields='ts_code,trade_date,close,pe,total_mv,circ_mv')\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            all_data.append(df)\n    except:\n        pass\n    \n    if (i+1) % 500 == 0:\n        print(f'{i+1}/{len(stocks)}')\n    time.sleep(0.08)\n\nif all_data:\n    result = pd.concat(all_data, ignore_index=True)\n    result.to_csv('data/daily_basic_all.csv', index=False)\n    print(f'OK: {len(result):,}')\n\"","timeout":1200}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25131,"output":342,"cacheRead":18402,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772505032279}}
