{"type":"message","id":"226d75f3","parentId":"f3813979","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:26:12.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问关于晚餐是否应该吃100克紫薯等碳水化合物的问题。今天她已经摄入了大量蛋白质和较低的热量。我需要根据她的增肌减脂目标给出建议。","thinkingSignature":"deff6db8a9970280a5761718df4e0380c9f256bc48f327d69d2193f37772212e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cd0nwnk8999q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && source .venv/bin/activate && python -c \"\nprint('今日总结:')\nprint('='*50)\nprint('蛋白质: ~90.7g (目标70-90g) ✅')\nprint()\nprint('热量缺口: ~1100大卡 (过大)')\nprint()\nprint('晚上建议:')\nprint('-'*50)\nprint('方案A: 不吃碳水')\nprint('  50g鸡胸肉 + 蔬菜')\nprint('  热量: ~150大卡')\nprint('  蛋白: ~15g')\nprint()\nprint('方案B: 吃碳水')\nprint('  50g鸡胸肉 + 100g紫薯 + 蔬菜')\nprint('  热量: ~300大卡')\nprint('  蛋白: ~15g + 碳水: ~20g')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":244,"cacheRead":8078,"cacheWrite":111808,"totalTokens":120166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772526351455}}
