{"type":"message","id":"5fc3c20c","parentId":"b9c23bca","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:36:59.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"cron任务已设置好。现在让我开始完善回测验证系统。需要更新最新数据。","thinkingSignature":"76558dae274b1e728ca6ebd98f90b2172af437f1b0e1c44199fc93c7573fee03"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **每日推送已设置！**\n\n| 任务 | 时间 | 状态 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| 量化日报 | 工作日 9:00 | ✅ 已启用 |\n| 健身提醒 | 工作日 11:30 | ✅ 已启用 |\n\n现在完善回测验证，先下载最新数据：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oll6340r1s8g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && source .venv/bin/activate && python -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nimport os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\nload_dotenv('config/.env.tushare')\n\npro = ts.pro_api(os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN'))\n\n# 更新指数数据\nprint('更新指数数据...')\nfor code in ['000300.SH', '000905.SH', '000852.SH', '000001.SH']:\n    df = pro.index_daily(ts_code=code, start_date='20200101')\n    if df is not None and len(df) > 0:\n        df.to_csv(f'data/index_{code.replace(\\\".\\\",\\\"_\\\")}.csv', index=False)\n        print(f'  {code}: {len(df)}条')\n\n# 更新股票数据\nprint('更新股票数据...')\nstocks = pd.read_csv('data/stock_basic.csv')['ts_code'].tolist()\nprint(f'  股票数: {len(stocks)}')\n\nprint('数据更新完成')\n\"","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":130925,"output":341,"cacheRead":18417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772552212303}}
