{"type":"message","id":"2db67c03","parentId":"a3af1d12","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:39:03.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"回测完成了！让我总结一下结果。","thinkingSignature":"4c4c151f8a959e453c52320a9e73d3b9579e37d92b7dae38004f64aad139fab4"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 完成！回测验证结果\n\n### 策略回测绩效\n\n| 策略 | 年化收益 | 胜率 | 夏普 | 最大回撤 |\n|-----|---------|------|------|---------|\n| **小市值轮动** | **76.49%** | 71.4% | 2.98 | -8.19% |\n| 动量策略 | 38.10% | 66.7% | 2.03 | 0% |\n| 中证1000(基准) | 43.44% | - | - | - |\n\n### 月度表现 (小市值)\n\n```\n2025/01: +10.00%  2025/02: +8.97%  2025/03: -0.74%\n2025/04: +4.90%   2025/05: +3.34%  2025/06: +8.23%\n2025/07: +6.21%   2025/08: +9.50%  2025/09: +5.32%\n2025/10: -3.00%   2025/11: -5.36%  2025/12: +9.42%\n2026/01: +14.32%  2026/02: -1.19%\n```\n\n### 已完成功能\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|-----|------|\n| 每日9点自动推送 | ✅ 已设置 |\n| 多策略选股 | ✅ 8个策略 |\n| 回测验证系统 | ✅ 已完成 |\n| 数据自动更新 | ✅ |\n\n### 提醒\n\n**明天9点**会收到第一份量化日报，包含：\n- 市场概况\n- 可转债双低 TOP5\n- 小市值A股 TOP10\n- 动量策略信号"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":134803,"output":404,"cacheRead":18417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772552332863}}
