{"type":"message","id":"b543c0ee","parentId":"0db1cdad","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:41:58.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我下载最近5年的数据，然后重新回测，并且要计算Alpha和Beta值。这需要：\n1. 下载2019-2026年的完整A股数据\n2. 重新运行回测\n3. 计算Alpha、Beta等指标\n\n让我开始下载数据。","thinkingSignature":"b4a32162163244ff82119b7fea1cd482fdf01c08f44d23725bdb3303385b7849"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cga3k0dhzux1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && source .venv/bin/activate && python -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nimport os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\nload_dotenv('config/.env.tushare')\n\npro = ts.pro_api(os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN'))\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('下载5年历史数据')\nprint('='*60)\n\n# 1. 更新指数数据 (2019-2026)\nprint('\\n1. 更新指数数据...')\nfor code in ['000300.SH', '000905.SH', '000852.SH', '000016.SH']:\n    print(f'  获取 {code}...')\n    df = pro.index_daily(ts_code=code, start_date='20190101')\n    if df is not None:\n        df.to_csv(f'data/index_{code.replace(\\\".\\\",\\\"_\\\")}.csv', index=False)\n        print(f'    完成: {len(df)}条')\n\n# 2. 获取股票列表\nprint('\\n2. 获取股票列表...')\nstocks = pro.stock_basic(list_status='L', fields='ts_code,symbol,name,area,industry,market')\nstocks = stocks[~stocks['name'].str.contains('ST|退', na=False)]\nstocks.to_csv('data/stock_basic.csv', index=False)\nprint(f'  股票数: {len(stocks)}')\n\n# 3. 批量获取日线数据\nprint('\\n3. 获取日线数据(2019-2026)...')\n# 获取所有股票的日线不太现实,先获取指数成分股\nprint('  获取主要指数成分股...')\n\n# 获取中证1000成分股\ntry:\n    index_stocks = pro.index_weight(ts_code='000852.SH', trade_date='20260302')\n    if index_stocks is not None:\n        print(f'  中证1000成分股: {len(index_stocks)}')\n        index_stocks.to_csv('data/index_1000_stocks.csv', index=False)\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'  获取失败: {e}')\n\nprint('\\n数据下载完成!')\n\"","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":546,"cacheRead":184