lose'].iloc[0] - 1) * 100\nannual3 = (1 + total_ret3/100) ** (1/5.2) - 1\nprint(f'  总收益: {total_ret3:.2f}%')\nprint(f'  年化: {annual3*100:.2f}%')\n\nprint('\\n' + '='*60)\nprint('结论')\nprint('='*60)\nprint('''\n如果想在5年内实现年化50%+收益，需要:\n\n1. 【高收益策略】\n   - 可转债双低轮动\n   - 小市值股票轮动\n   - 动量策略\n\n2. 【加杠杆】\n   - 融资融券 (风险极大!)\n   - 期货/期权\n\n3. 【时间换空间】\n   - 年化20-30%已经很好\n   - 50%需要极高风险\n\n⚠️ 警告: 年化50%意味着5年57倍,非常人所能及\n''')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":138902,"output":893,"cacheRead":18417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772552572320}}
